{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:26:59.322498+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14e35346190d0ff04ea56d634a34dbac593ed1c9)", "id": "lc_bc1ce993-5ba5-4b99-971d-4051e5c876f7"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"name\": \"vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"description\": \"Vue.js 3 Vite starter template with Pinia, Vue Router, Bootstrap and more.\",\n  \"version\": \"0.0.0-semantic-release\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\",\n  \"repository\": \"https://github.com/kouts/vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\",\n    \"dev\": \"vite\",\n    \"build\": \"vite build\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n    \"build-preview\": \"vite build && vite preview\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"lint-fix\": \"eslint --fix \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"test:unit\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:unit-coverage\": \"vitest run --coverage\",\n    \"prepare\": \"husky\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"bootstrap\": \"^5.3.8\",\n    \"jsdom\": \"^27.1.0\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^3.0.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.0.6\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.6.3\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@commitlint/cli\": \"^20.1.0\",\n    \"@commitlint/config-conventional\": \"^20.0.0\",\n    \"@fullhuman/postcss-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@fullhuman/vue-cli-plugin-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@kouts/eslint-config\": \"^3.0.9\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-vue\": \"^6.0.1\",\n    \"@vue/compiler-sfc\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"@vue/test-utils\": \"^2.4.6\",\n    \"autoprefixer\": \"^10.4.21\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.0\",\n    \"husky\": \"^9.1.7\",\n    \"lint-staged\": \"^16.2.6\",\n    \"prettier\": \"^3.6.2\",\n    \"sass\": \"^1.93.3\",\n    \"vite\": \"^7.1.12\",\n    \"vite-plugin-html\": \"^3.2.2\"\n  }\n}", "id": "lc_db52402d-b693-4633-a557-76b58abaf6b1"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "ef653ed0-3d0c-4bec-b841-44bf3faafa7e", "tool_call_id": "call_00_JMtdptrGtrxg6cyOwZWC4345", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:26:59.476082+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_803036af-f9c1-4d6b-a02b-725b93d4fa35"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# vue3-vite-starter-template\n\nA single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n\n**Features**\n\n- Vitest for unit testing\n- Pinia for state management\n- Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n- Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n- SCSS variables inside Vue components\n- Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n- Basic multiple layouts feature\n- ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n- Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n\n## Project setup\n\n```\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n\n```\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Compiles and minifies for production\n\n```\npnpm run build\n```\n\n## Run your unit tests\n\n```\npnpm run test:unit\n```\n\n### Lints files\n\n```\npnpm run lint\n```\n\n### Lints and fixes files\n\n```\nnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n### Customize configuration\n\nSee [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).\n", "id": "lc_a963f4a7-cb0c-41e4-a2da-a1cc9c0ea55b"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "2e3a83d9-b248-4cb4-ab6f-c6fa8403041d", "tool_call_id": "call_01_c6VBlDOi1XG1tlrBK3m56685", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:27:03.049075+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Setup and Day-to-Day Development Commands\n\nBased on the repository's `package.json` scripts and `README.md`, here are the commands:\n\n### Setup / Install\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n(Note: The project enforces `pnpm` as the package manager via a `preinstall` script that runs `npx only-allow pnpm`.)\n\n### Development Server (hot-reloads)\n```bash\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Production Build\n```bash\npnpm run build\n```\n\n### Preview Production Build\n```bash\npnpm run preview\n# or combined: pnpm run build-preview\n```\n\n### Unit Tests\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit\n```\n\n### Unit Tests with Coverage\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit-coverage\n```\n\n### Lint\n```bash\npnpm run lint\n```\n\n### Lint and Fix\n```bash\npnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n### Other notable commands (from scripts)\n- `pnpm run prepare` – Sets up husky git hooks\n- `pnpm run dev` uses **Vite** dev server\n- `pnpm run build` uses **Vite** to build\n- `pnpm run test:unit` uses **Vitest** (a Vite-native test runner)\n- `pnpm run lint` uses **ESLint** on `.vue`, `.ts`, `.js` files\n\nThe README also lists `npm run lint-fix` but the actual script in `package.json` is `lint-fix` (using `pnpm`). Either way, it runs `eslint --fix`.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 366, "prompt_tokens": 4499, "total_tokens": 4865, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 23, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 3584}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 3584, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 915}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "696e9e3b-62df-428e-8f81-f403468e020b", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea469-3794-72c3-8ba2-81ad13e4c354-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 4499, "output_tokens": 366, "total_tokens": 4865, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 3584}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 23}}}}]}}}
